rows.label: tlk70000023_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Adel-sama, Laura-sama.
I have decided to stay here.

rows.label: tlk70000023_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I was born in Iira and grew up here, 
and I think this is where I want my
bones to rest too.

rows.label: tlk70000023_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I was born from the Divine Beast and
to the Divine Beast I shall return. That's my
final wish.

rows.label: tlk70000023_05_msg0004
rows.name:
So please... If you should fail to defeat
the Holy Grail, think of it as fate...

rows.label: tlk70000023_05_msg0005
rows.name: But give the fight everything you've got!
